OL,3,CKing presents D-Day veteran with 100th
OL,4,Cbirthday card at Buckingham Palace
OL,6,FA D-Day veteran was "surprised and
OL,7,Fdelighted" to be invited to Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace where he was presented with his
OL,9,F100th birthday card from the King.
OL,11,FJim Miller, who turned 100 on June 1,
OL,12,Flanded on the Normandy beaches in June
OL,13,F1944 and took part in the Allied
OL,14,Fmilitary operation to liberate
OL,15,Foccupied France and western Europe.
OL,17,FHe said: "I was totally surprised and
OL,18,Fdelighted to be invited to Buckingham
OL,19,FPalace!
