OL,3,CKing presents D-Day veteran with 100th
OL,4,Cbirthday card at Buckingham Palace
OL,6,F"It was a special day and a real
OL,7,Fhonour for me to meet the King and be
OL,8,Fpresented with my 100th birthday card.
OL,10,F"I am humbled to reach such a great
OL,11,Fnumber, especially when I think of
OL,12,Fthose who fell on the Normandy beaches
OL,13,Fall those years ago.
OL,15,F"The King was very interested to hear
OL,16,Fabout my military service and personal
OL,17,Fexperience of such a momentous and
OL,18,Fharrowing time.
